Sentencas: As a promising energy conversion device, solid oxide cell can realize efficient conversion between chemical energy and electrical energy under solid oxide fuel cell and solid oxide electrolysis cell mode.
Titulo: Unveiling dual functional catalytic performance of Pr1.5La0.5Ni0.8Cu0.2O4+s air electrode for solid oxide cells

Sentencas: In this work, a Ruddlesden-Popper type oxide Pr1.5La0.5Ni0.8Cu0.2O4+delta (PLNC) with good mixed ionic-electronic conductivity is investigated as a dual functional air electrode for SOC.
Titulo: Unveiling dual functional catalytic performance of Pr1.5La0.5Ni0.8Cu0.2O4+s air electrode for solid oxide cells

Sentencas: The results confirm that the peak power densities of the LSGM electrolyte supported cell with PLNC-GDC composite air electrode can reach 1.127, 0.911, 0.675 and 0.446 W cm-2 at 800, 750, 700 and 650 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Unveiling dual functional catalytic performance of Pr1.5La0.5Ni0.8Cu0.2O4+s air electrode for solid oxide cells

Sentencas: Meanwhile, the cell possesses excellent durability for nearly 200 h under a constant current density of 400 mA cm-2 at 700 degrees C. The cell also shows superior electrolysis current density of 1.54 A cm-2 under electrolysis voltage of 1.3 V at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Unveiling dual functional catalytic performance of Pr1.5La0.5Ni0.8Cu0.2O4+s air electrode for solid oxide cells

Sentencas: The study demonstrates that PLNC is a promising dual functional air electrode material with excellent oxygen reduction reaction and oxygen evolution reaction activity for oxygen electrocatalytic reaction.
Titulo: Unveiling dual functional catalytic performance of Pr1.5La0.5Ni0.8Cu0.2O4+s air electrode for solid oxide cells
